        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">If you are using deflux and vexxing in your regular line up, regen means little.  No one taps to exactly their hp limit.  They always spill over, which basically negates any benefit of regen.</P><P>Regen is most useful when parked out in nowhere, soloing things.</P><P>For mana gaining, ideally the best thing to do is to get items with flowing thought 1 and another with flowing thought 2.  But if you are able to get those items, you are not caring so much about downtime.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
